title: HOUR 1 - Cowboys-Giants, Davante Adams
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Cowboys-Giants, Davante Adams
description:
Colin gives the Cowboys credit for winning 2 games in a row with a backup QB

The Giants might have found the right head coach finally

Davante Adams leaving Aaron Rodgers and the Packers for the Raiders was a move that left both sides in a worse position

 

Guest: Matt Mosley
